            "size": 2016,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"result\":{\"asin\":\"B0GHR6QBK7\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41x1iNgM01L._SS180_.jpg\",\"productTitle\":\"INNOSURE [3-PACK] Silicone Case x1, HD Clear Tempered Glass Screen Protector 1.9\\\" x2 for Garmin inReach Mini 3, Anti-Drop, Anti Static, Non-Slip, Durable (Silicone Case (Black) + Glass (HD Clear))\",\"featureBullets\":[\"Exclusive Custom Design: Engineered specifically for Garmin inReach Mini 3, this optimized design ensures seamless integration with all device functions and controls, specifically features an integrated cutout for Spine Mount Adapter, and full coverage design for the antenna area with thickness-reduced treatment\",\"2x HD Clear Glass Screen Protector: Crafted from aluminum silicate dual-tempered glass, this premium material offers superior scratch, crack, and impact resistance for maximum device's screen protection. The high-end oleophobic coating repels fingerprints, smudges, and liquid residues while maintaining screen clarity.\",\"1xSilicone case: Durable, shock-absorbent eco-friendly silicone protects against drops, impacts, and scratches during rugged outdoor rides. Maintaining full access to buttons, ports and the charging interface through strategically placed cutouts. Anti static coating provides a good hand feel and effectively prevents dust adsorption.\",\"Installation Guide: Apply Tempered Glass First - Clean the screen thoroughly to prevent bubbles, aligning edges precisely (similar to phone screen protector installation). Next attach the Case - Secure the silicone case by snapping the bottom edge into place first, followed by the top. Ensure the screen protector remains aligned to avoid shifting.\",\"for Gamin inReach Mini 3 protective case cover, tempered glass screen protector accessories.\"],\"byLineContributors\":[\"INNOSURE\"],\"catalogSize\":null,\"taxCurrency\":\"USD\",\"taxValue\":15.88,\"promotionId\":\"A1PTFYTMELDTGW\",\"purchasePolicyCode\":\"AmazonVine\",\"asinTangoEligible\":true,\"productSiteLaunchDate\":1768895628078,\"limitedQuantity\":false},\"error\":null}"
          },
