          "content": {
            "size": 2149,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"result\":{\"asin\":\"B0GLYFCTXC\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/31NeSVeJuGL._SS180_.jpg\",\"productTitle\":\"231807 (NT-40) Furnace Limit Switch – Replacement RV Furnace Limit Switch for Suburban RV Furnaces SF-20/SF-30/SF-40/SF-42/NT-16SE/NT-20SE/NT-30SE/NT30-SB/NT-40SE/NT-20SEQ /NT-40SEQ\",\"featureBullets\":[\"Fit for Suburban RV Furnaces:Compatible with a wide range of Suburban RV furnace models including SF-20, SF-30, SF-40, SF-42, NT-16SE, NT-20SE, NT-30SE, NT-40SE, NT-20SEQ, NT-30SEQ, and NT-40SEQ. Also suitable for Suburban NT-40 and NT30-SB units.The 231807 (NT-40) limit switch serves as a direct replacement part, ensuring seamless integration and reliable operation within your RV’s heating system.\",\"Premium Quality & Long-Lasting Durability:Constructed from high-grade, heat-resistant materials such as anodized aluminum and zinc-finished steel, this limit switch is built to endure extreme temperatures and rugged RV environments. It provides consistent performance and dependable safety cutoff functionality, making it ideal for long-term use in demanding conditions.\",\"Ensures Safe & Reliable Operation:As a critical component for RV furnace safety, the 231807 limit switch accurately monitors and controls internal temperatures to prevent overheating. Its robust design ensures a tight, leak-free connection and stable performance, giving you peace of mind on the road.\",\"Plug & Play Installation:Engineered for an exact fit, this 1-piece furnace limit switch matches OEM specifications and installs effortlessly into furnace assemblies—no modifications required. Simply remove the old switch and replace it with this high-quality part in minutes.\",\"Customer Support :If you have any questions before or after purchase, please don’t hesitate to contact us. We’re committed to providing prompt and helpful assistance to ensure your complete satisfaction.\"],\"byLineContributors\":[\"BKIFU\"],\"catalogSize\":null,\"taxCurrency\":\"USD\",\"taxValue\":15.99,\"promotionId\":\"A3DTPWW0Y8KUIJ\",\"purchasePolicyCode\":\"AmazonVine\",\"asinTangoEligible\":true,\"productSiteLaunchDate\":1770367188582,\"limitedQuantity\":true},\"error\":null}"
          },
